    ) -> Dict[str, Any]:
        """
        Update an NPC's emotional state with full context and side effects.
        
        Args:
            npc_id: ID of the NPC
            emotion: Primary emotion to set (e.g., "joy", "anger", "fear")
            intensity: Intensity of the emotion (0.0-1.0)
