        npc_action: Dict[str, Any]
    ) -> Dict[str, Any]:
        """
        Update relationship based on an interaction with enhanced error handling
        and memory integration.
        
        Args:
            npc_id: ID of the NPC
            entity_type: Type of entity ("npc" or "player")
